              <subprov skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
                <para>
                  <text>After the date on which the Whirinaki agreement ends, any references to determinations referred to in <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (1)</citation></changeable> must be read as references to the Authority making a reserve supply determination, or rescinding a reserve supply determination, as the case requires.</text>
